om\": 688, \"to\": 700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was going to get out and enjoy the atmosphere, and that's the best you can do for yourself.\\\"\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the atmosphere\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not that McKeown won that was most impressive.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McKeown\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was that she had the gauntlet thrown down in front of her by a former champion and a world record ripped away.\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gauntlet\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 894}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 915}, {\"ngram\": \"a former champion\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 943}, {\"ngram\": \"a world record\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And she did not even blink.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1004, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McKeown was all business when she came out of the tunnel, marching to her block with eyes only on the prize at stake.\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McKeown\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"business\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"the tunnel\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"her block\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1085}, {\"ngram\": \"eyes\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"the prize\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1113}, {\"ngram\": \"stake\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The nerves were definitely there,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The nerves\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I reminded myself that it's a pool in a different venue, and I train every single day of my life.\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": [], \"